                            <comment id="56218" author="adilger" created="Fri, 12 Apr 2013 18:22:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mike, this is a release blocker, because this check breaks the build after 2.3.90.  Can you please take a look and submit a patch?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
